import numpy as np
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
# create a uniform array of values from -10.0 to 10.0 and create 100000 instances of it
values = np.random.uniform(-10.0, 10.0, 100000)
plt.hist(values, 50)
plt.show()

plt.show()
